{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06","title":"Lesson 6 - Add a property binding to a component’s template","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\" translation-result=\"on\">第 6 課 - 將屬性繫結新增到元件的範本中<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Lesson 6 - Add a property binding to a component’s template<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">這節課示範瞭如何將屬性繫結新增到範本中並透過它將動態資料傳給元件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This tutorial lesson demonstrates how to add property binding to a template and use it to pass dynamic data to components.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><strong>所需時間：</strong> 完成這節課預計需要 5 分鐘左右。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><strong>Time required:</strong> expect to spend about 5 minutes to complete this lesson.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"before-you-start\" translation-result=\"on\">開始之前<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#before-you-start\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Before you start<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#before-you-start\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">這節課以上一課的程式碼為起點，你可以：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This lesson starts with the code from the previous lesson, so you can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在整合開發環境（IDE）中使用你在第 5 課中建立的程式碼。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the code that you created in Lesson 5 in your integrated development environment (IDE).</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">從上一課的程式碼範例開始。選擇<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-05\"></live-example>，以便：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Start with the code example from the previous lesson. Choose the <live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-05\"></live-example> from Lesson 5 where you can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 StackBlitz 中的<em>線上例子</em>，其中 StackBlitz 的介面就是你的 IDE。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the <em>live example</em> in StackBlitz, where the StackBlitz interface is your IDE.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用<em>下載範例</em>並在你的 IDE 中開啟它。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the <em>download example</em> and open it in your IDE.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你還沒看過簡介，請存取 <a href=\"tutorial/first-app\">Angular 課程簡介</a>以確保你已具備完成這節課所需的一切知識。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If you haven't reviewed the introduction, visit the <a href=\"tutorial/first-app\">Introduction to Angular tutorial</a> to make sure you have everything you need to complete this lesson.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你在這節課中遇到任何問題，可以檢視這節課的完整程式碼，參見<live-example></live-example>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If you have any trouble during this lesson, you can review the completed code for this lesson, in the <live-example></live-example> for this lesson.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"after-you-finish\" translation-result=\"on\">完成之後<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#after-you-finish\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">After you finish<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#after-you-finish\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">應用程式在 <code>HomeComponent</code> 範本中具有一些資料繫結。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Your app has data bindings in the <code>HomeComponent</code> template.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">應用程式將資料從 <code>HomeComponent</code> 傳送到 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Your app sends data from the <code>HomeComponent</code> to the <code>HousingLocationComponent</code>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"conceptual-preview-of-inputs\" translation-result=\"on\">輸入屬性的概念性預覽<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Conceptual preview of Inputs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在第 5 課中，你將 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 裝飾器新增到 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 中的屬性上，以允許元件接收資料。在這節課中，你將透過將資料繫結到範本中的那些屬性來從父元件向子元件共享資料。Angular 中有多種形式的資料繫結，在這節課中，你將使用屬性繫結。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In lesson 5, you added <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> decorators to properties in the <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> allow the component to receive data. In this lesson, you'll continue the process of sharing data from the parent component to the child component by binding data to those properties in the template. There are several forms of data binding in Angular, in this lesson you'll use property binding.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">屬性繫結能讓你將變數連線到 Angular 範本中的 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> 屬性。然後把資料動態繫結到此 <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Property binding enables you to connect a variable to an <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code> in an Angular template. The data is then dynamically bound to the <code><a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a></code>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">更深入的解釋，請參閱<a href=\"guide/property-binding\">屬性繫結</a>指南。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For a more in depth explanation, please refer to the <a href=\"guide/property-binding\">Property binding</a> guide.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"lesson-steps\" translation-result=\"on\">課程步驟<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Lesson steps<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 IDE 中對應用程式程式碼執行下列步驟。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Perform these steps on the app code in your IDE.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\" translation-result=\"on\">第 1 步 - 更新 <code>HomeComponent</code> 範本中的 <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> 標記<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Step 1 - Update <app-housing-location> tag in the <code>HomeComponent</code> template</app-housing-location><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">此步驟將屬性繫結新增到 <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> 標記上。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This step adds property binding to the <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> tag.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在程式碼編輯器中：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In the code editor:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">導航到 <code>src/app/home/home.component.ts</code></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Navigate to <code>src/app/home/home.component.ts</code></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 裝飾器的範本屬性中，把程式碼更新成這樣：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In the template property of the <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> decorator, update the code to match the code below:</p>\n\n<code-example header=\"Add housingLocation property binding\" path=\"first-app-lesson-06/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"add-property-binding\">\n&lt;app-housing-location [housingLocation]=\"housingLocation\"&gt;&lt;/app-housing-location&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當向元件標籤新增屬性繫結時，我們使用 <code>[attribute] = \"value\"</code> 語法來通知 Angular 所賦的值應該視為來自元件類別的屬性，而不是字串值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When adding a property binding to a component tag, we use the <code>[attribute] = \"value\"</code> syntax to notify Angular that the assigned value should be treated as a property from the component class and not a string value.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">右側的值是 <code>HomeComponent</code> 中的屬性名稱。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The value on the right handside is the name of the property from the <code>HomeComponent</code>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\" translation-result=\"on\">第 2 步 - 確認程式碼仍然能工作<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Step 2 - Confirm the code still works<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">儲存你的更改並確認應用程式沒有任何錯誤。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Save your changes and confirm the app does not have any errors.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在繼續下一步之前更正所有錯誤。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Correct any errors before you continue to the next step.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" translation-result=\"on\">課程回顧<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Lesson review<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在這節課中，你添加了一個新的屬性繫結，並傳入了對類屬性的參考。現在，<code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 就能存取可用來在自訂元件中顯示的資料了。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In this lesson, you added a new property binding and passed in a reference to a class property. Now, the <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> has access to data that it can use to customize the component's display.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你在學習這節課時遇到了任何問題，可以在<live-example></live-example>檢視完整程式碼。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If you are having any trouble with this lesson, you can review the completed code for it in the <live-example></live-example>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Next steps<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\">第 7 課 - 向元件範本新增插值</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\">Lesson 7 - Add an interpolation to a component’s template</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\" translation-result=\"on\">有關這節課中涵蓋的主題的更多資訊，請存取：<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">For more information about the topics covered in this lesson, visit:<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">屬性繫結</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">Property binding</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-05\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/property-binding\n - tutorial/first-app\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#after-you-finish\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#before-you-start\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#conceptual-preview-of-inputs\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-6---add-a-property-binding-to-a-components-template\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#lesson-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-1---update--tag-in-the-homecomponent-template\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#step-2---confirm-the-code-still-works\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#下一步\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#完成之後\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#開始之前\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#有關這節課中涵蓋的主題的更多資訊請存取\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#第-1-步---更新-homecomponent-範本中的-app-housing-location-標記\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#第-2-步---確認程式碼仍然能工作\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#第-6-課---將屬性繫結新增到元件的範本中\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#課程回顧\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#課程步驟\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06#輸入屬性的概念性預覽\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-06.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}